## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c0c9-138">次の例は、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>から継承し、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId> およびを使用するカスタム音声合成実装の一部です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c0c9-138">The example below is part of a custom speech synthesis implementation inheriting from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, and using the use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span></span>  
  
